Describe the project or task Alta Vista Technology helped with:
Sage Intacct Implementation project from QuickBooks Desktop.

What do you like best about Alta Vista Technology?
Knowledgeable team members on system configuration and report-building;
Alta Vista was actively managing the project and was able to provide me guidance on priorities and issues;
Automated detail data conversion/migration from QB database to Sage Intacct that could have taken days, if not weeks, to complete.

What do you dislike about Alta Vista Technology?
We used Microsoft Teams as the project tracking tool. It might be good for one that does not use Teams in work.

What problems is Alta Vista Technology solving and how is that benefiting you?
- Consolidated reporting with all entities - much less Excel consolidation work;
- Timely report updates on most recent data - much less report extraction effort from QB;
- Inventory control process baseline established;
